1. *Razvod* je teška odluka za svakog čoveka. (Divorce is a difficult decision for every man.)

2. Oni su se odlučili da se *razvedu* posle dugogodišnje veze. (They decided to get divorced after a long relationship.)

3. Par se *razvodi* zbog različitih očekivanja. (The couple is divorcing due to different expectations.)

4. Ona je priznala da je njen *razvod* bio izazvan nevernošću. (She admitted that her divorce was caused by infidelity.)

5. On je dobio pravo da se *razvede* kako bi se oženio drugom ženom. (He was granted the right to divorce in order to marry another woman.)